<h2>Online Help for HBL SELLING/BUYING Object</h2>
<br></br>
  
This is an Object to manage the selling rate to customers and the buying rates from service suppliers.<br></br>
Also to manage the payment(payable to service provider and receivable from the customers).<br></br>
<br></br>
1.All LISTS:  -Show all the HB/L SELLING/BUYING items in the list<br></br>
2.Payment Process-Standard(ID) : -View to process payment for both selling and buying <br></br>
3.Payment Process-Receiving :-View to process payment-receiving(selling)<br></br>
4.Payable(B)Process- Standard(ID) : -View to process payment-paying(buying)<br></br>
Master Payment-Consolidation allocation :- -View to check and modify the consolidation cost allocation items<br></br>
Partner Settlement-Payable Remained: for processing the settlement between partner(buying)<br></br>
Partner Settlement- Receivables remained: For processing the settlement between partner(selling)<br></br>
Payment process-Payable to vendor-H B/L: View to process the payment to local vendor<br></br>
Receivable from Domestic client: View to confirm the receivable from customer left<br></br>
Tax Confirmation view: View to filter the certain tax-type of selling/buying items<br></br>
<br></br>

Setup Field: BANK ACCCOUNT TRANSFERED TO-SELLING<br></br>
==>the bank list must be registered as Picklist<br></br>
<br></br>


Exchange rate<br></br>
==>Selling exchange rate and Buying exchange rate are syncronized if the below condition met.<br></br>
1. Import: ETA is inbetween Start Date and End date of Exchange rate.<br></br>
2. Export: ETD is inbetween Start Date and End date of Exchange rate.<br></br>
